story_teamgalactic_01_09000/2401_1201_01:
I heard that some brats were making a fuss right
in our hideout.
story_teamgalactic_01_09000/2401_1201_02: We’ll get rid of you for Master Cyrus!
story_teamgalactic_01_09000/2401_1201_03: Wait! Do you even know what he’s trying to do?
story_teamgalactic_01_09000/2401_1201_05:
Master Cyrus is trying to change the world for the
better! For all of us!
story_teamgalactic_01_09000/2401_1201_06:
Wake up, would you?! That’s not even close to
the truth!
story_teamgalactic_01_09000/2401_1201_07:
If he carries out his plan, you might get erased
from this world, you know!
story_teamgalactic_01_09000/2401_1201_08:
Save your breath. Our master’s methods are
beyond reproach!
story_teamgalactic_01_09000/2401_1201_09:
There’s no way anything wrong will happen if we
stick with Master Cyrus!
story_teamgalactic_01_09000/2401_1201_10: It’s no good. We’re not getting through to them.
story_teamgalactic_01_09000/2401_1201_11:
Are we not going to be able to solve this by
reasoning with them?
